@startuml Authentication Sub-Diagram

title LebanonConnect — Authentication Flow Detail

actor "Guest"               as Guest
actor "Authenticated User"  as AuthUser

rectangle "Authentication Subsystem" {

  usecase "Register"           as UC_Register
  usecase "Login"              as UC_Login
  usecase "Authenticate User"  as UC_Auth
  usecase "JWT Validation"     as UC_JWT

}

Guest     --> UC_Register
Guest     --> UC_Login

AuthUser  --> UC_Auth

UC_Auth   ..> UC_JWT      : <<include>>

note right of UC_Register
  POST /api/auth/register
  - Email uniqueness check
  - Password bcrypt hash (salt=10)
  - Role: customer | provider
  - Creates role-specific profile doc
end note

note right of UC_Login
  POST /api/auth/login
  - Finds active user by email
  - bcrypt.compare password
  - Signs JWT (payload: id, role)
  - Expiry: 7 days
end note

note right of UC_Auth
  requireAuth middleware:
  - Extracts Bearer token from header
  - Calls jwt.verify(token, JWT_SECRET)
  - Confirms user still active in DB
  - Attaches decoded {id, role} to req.user
end note

note right of UC_JWT
  jsonwebtoken library
  - Algorithm: HS256 (default)
  - Secret: process.env.JWT_SECRET
  - Throws JsonWebTokenError on tamper
  - Throws TokenExpiredError after 7d
end note

skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor     #F9A825
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #FCE4EC
  BorderColor     #C62828
}

@enduml
